  <a class="cta-button" href="/enquiry">Get a Survey Quote</a>
  </div>
  </section><!-- MAIN CONTENT SECTION --><section class="service-detail">
  <div class="box-container">
  <h2>Your Independent Surveyor in Christleton</h2>
  <p>
          Based nearby in Connah’s Quay, I regularly serve Christleton and surrounding villages with detailed RICS Home Surveys, damp inspections and ventilation checks. Whether you're buying a period cottage or modern detached home, I offer unbiased guidance and practical advice.
        </p>
  <h2>Christleton Surveying Services</h2>
  <ul>
  <li><strong>RICS Level 1 Condition Report:</strong> Entry-level survey for newer, well-maintained homes.</li>
  <li><strong>RICS Level 2 HomeBuyer Survey:</strong> Popular option for standard homes—includes repair advice and condition ratings.</li>
  <li><strong>RICS Level 3 Building Survey:</strong> The most detailed option—essential for older, extended or altered properties.</li>
  <li><strong>Damp &amp; Timber Inspections:</strong> Identify and understand moisture issues, mould or decay.</li>
  <li><strong>Residential Ventilation Assessments:</strong> Diagnose poor airflow, indoor humidity and condensation risk.</li>
  <li><strong>Measured Floorplans:</strong> Scaled drawings for planning, marketing or renovation.</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>Why Choose LEM Building Surveying?</h2>
  <ul>
  <li><strong>AssocRICS-qualified surveyor:</strong> All surveys carried out by Liam personally.</li>
  <li><strong>Fast turnaround:</strong> Reports usually delivered within 3–5 working days.</li>
  <li><strong>Local knowledge:</strong> Familiar with property types and construction in Christleton, Vicars Cross and south Chester.</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>Get a Quote or Ask for Advice</h2>
  <p>
          Whether you’re exploring your options or ready to book, I’m happy to help. No pressure, no sales — just honest, expert advice.
        </p>
  <div class="cta-section">
  <a class="cta-button" href="/enquiry">Request a Survey</a>
